      "id": "dungeon_asher_tower",
      "name": "Asher's Tower",
      "name_fr": "Tour d'Asher",
      "description": "A tower built over a major Fissure by the Asher family, now corrupted from within. What began as a bastion of protection has become a site of profane rituals — Edric, guided by his advisor Sevik, dug into the Fissure believing he could purify it. Instead, their excavations amplified the corruption, spreading Fissures across the entire region — all the way to your village of Kanarion.",
      "description_fr": "Une tour construite sur une Fissure majeure par la famille d'Asher, desormais corrompue de l'interieur. Ce qui etait un bastion de protection est devenu un lieu de rituels profanes — Edric, guide par son conseiller Sevik, a creuse dans la Fissure en croyant la purifier. Au lieu de cela, leurs excavations ont amplifie la corruption, propageant les Fissures dans toute la region — jusqu'a votre village de Kanarion.",
      "level_range": [
